<h2>Why People Are Buying Oura Ring Gen 3</h2>
<p>Most people don't sleep well and don't know why. Smartwatches track sleep but are uncomfortable to wear at night. The Oura Ring became popular because it promises lab-quality sleep tracking in a ring you forget you're wearing.</p>

<h2>What Is Oura Ring Gen 3?</h2>
<p>The Oura Ring Gen 3 is a titanium smart ring with sensors for heart rate, HRV, body temperature, and blood oxygen. It syncs with a mobile app to provide daily readiness scores and sleep analysis. It went viral when athletes and biohackers praised its accuracy.</p>
<p><strong>Why it went viral:</strong> Biohacker and athlete endorsements on podcasts and social media</p>

<h2>How to Use Oura Ring Gen 3</h2>
<ol>
