    <li><strong>2.</strong> Download the Oura app and pair the ring via Bluetooth</li>
    <li><strong>3.</strong> Wear the ring continuously — it tracks sleep, activity, and recovery automatically</li>
    <li><strong>4.</strong> Check your daily Readiness, Sleep, and Activity scores each morning in the app</li>
